3. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) - The paper applies the algorithm to game-based hyper-parameter optimisation problems, which is a common area of research in game theory. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The NTBEA is an evolutionary algorithm, which is a common technique in evolutionary computing. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper describes an optimisation algorithm for noisy and expensive discrete optimisation problems, which is a common area of research in systems and control.
